  - Ward food & brew lines in 52 / 53 / 58.
  - Wardstone-related projects and rituals in 57.

When implemented:

- Use B159 as checklist:

  - Subterranean Wardstone arena built? ✔
  - Phases (flicker → inverted glyphs → merge) working? ✔
  - Loot yields correct brackets/crust/essences/core/tendrils? ✔
  - Lodge projects and rituals consume those reagents in a meaningful way? ✔
